NAME
       wvCleanLatex - convert msword documents to LaTeX

SYNOPSIS
       wvCleanLatex in_word_doc out_latex_doc

DESCRIPTION
       wvCleanLatex  converts  word  documents  into LaTeX that
       looks like it'd been hand-edited
